snippet.title: Total War: PHARAOH - DYNASTIES - Battles
snippet.description:
Lethality, visibility, trajectories, oh my! Join Steve as he catches up with Milcho Vasilev from the Total War: PHARAOH dev team about Dynasties updated battles!

TOTAL WAR: PHARAOH AVAILABLE NOW - https://store.totalwar.com/en/total-war/total-war-pharaoh
